{"data":{"article":{},"attachments":{},"author_id":"1741993395910811648","conversation_id":"1866756608967201168","created_at":"2025-07-31T11:37:49.000Z","edit_controls":{"editable_until":"2025-07-31T12:37:49.000Z","edits_remaining":5,"is_edit_eligible":false},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["1950883595943575985"],"entities":{"mentions":[{"end":8,"id":"1561334508212723713","start":0,"username":"VVV8964"}]},"geo":{},"id":"1950883595943575985","in_reply_to_user_id":"1561334508212723713","lang":"zh","note_tweet":{"entities":{}},"possibly_sensitive":false,"public_metrics":{"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"reply_count":0,"retweet_count":0},"referenced_tweets":[{"id":"1866756608967201168","type":"replied_to"}],"reply_settings":"everyone","text":"@VVV8964 用石板和灯泡对话...想起了太空漫游，感觉这个场景挺有象征意味的，为什么我trip里没有这些突发奇想的点子（）"},"includes":{"tweets":[{"article":{},"attachments":{},"author_id":"1741993395910811648","conversation_id":"1866756608967201168","created_at":"2025-07-31T11:37:49.000Z","edit_controls":{"editable_until":"2025-07-31T12:37:49.000Z","edits_remaining":5,"is_edit_eligible":false},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["1950883595943575985"],"entities":{"mentions":[{"end":8,"id":"1561334508212723713","start":0,"username":"VVV8964"}]},"geo":{},"id":"1950883595943575985","in_reply_to_user_id":"1561334508212723713","lang":"zh","note_tweet":{"entities":{}},"possibly_sensitive":false,"public_metrics":{"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"reply_count":0,"retweet_count":0},"referenced_tweets":[{"id":"1866756608967201168","type":"replied_to"}],"reply_settings":"everyone","text":"@VVV8964 用石板和灯泡对话...想起了太空漫游，感觉这个场景挺有象征意味的，为什么我trip里没有这些突发奇想的点子（）"},{"article":{},"attachments":{},"author_id":"1561334508212723713","conversation_id":"1866756608967201168","created_at":"2024-12-11T08:07:12.000Z","edit_controls":{"editable_until":"2024-12-11T09:07:12.000Z","edits_remaining":5,"is_edit_eligible":true},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["1866756608967201168"],"entities":{"urls":[{"description":"概括：我由于现实生活不如意，翘课空腹吃了1g蘑菇，试图用蘑菇治疗我的抑郁症。与上次简单欣快的旅程不一样，这次的旅程压倒性地强大，并且复杂，深刻，朴实，但是不但没有即时缓解我的抑郁症，反而带来了恐怖的幻觉（Bad trip），似乎还让我持续一段时间更难入睡了。有人说短时间的bad trip长远来看是最有益的，目前现在是trip后一个月，我目前没有感觉到有压倒性的抑郁症，可能是真的有效果，也可能要归功于我间歇的医学计量的普瑞巴林治疗焦虑。这次旅程让我意识到，和娱乐性药物相反，迷幻药不能在生活不如意的时候吃，因为使用者要持续被迫面对全人类共有的最深刻的个人问题和存在焦虑。这可能让迷幻药更适合预防而不是治疗抑郁发作，可能氯胺酮等解离剂更适合抑郁症犯了吃，但是我应该是不会碰的。 正文： 为了避免恶心，我空腹伴着柠檬姜茶服用了1g蘑菇，然而这也使得药效更加强烈，三十分钟后看到闭眼幻觉。 我首先播放了小黄人电影的歌曲中“happy”进入旅程，导致我看到了很多卡通的幻觉，占据整个视野的曲线，纹理和图案，比如数十条波浪线从左上角摇晃到右下角，每个波浪上都有同样的人物。我看到了一些滑稽，荒谬，猎奇，诡异的人物，我甚至看到了一些…","display_url":"telegra.ph/1g%E8%BF%B7%E5…","end":52,"expanded_url":"https://telegra.ph/1g%E8%BF%B7%E5%B9%BB%E8%98%91%E8%8F%87-%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%E4%B8%80%E5%88%87-12-11","start":29,"status":200,"title":"1g迷幻蘑菇 理解一切","unwound_url":"https://telegra.ph/1g%E8%BF%B7%E5%B9%BB%E8%98%91%E8%8F%87-%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%E4%B8%80%E5%88%87-12-11","url":"https://t.co/7XmgmmZfld"}]},"geo":{},"id":"1866756608967201168","lang":"zh","note_tweet":{"entities":{}},"possibly_sensitive":false,"public_metrics":{"bookmark_count":4,"impression_count":6399,"like_count":14,"quote_count":1,"reply_count":1,"retweet_count":1},"reply_settings":"everyone","text":"发一下之前的蘑菇报告，修修改改了一个月，老样子，随便转载\nhttps://t.co/7XmgmmZfld"}],"users":[{"created_at":"2024-01-02T01:22:57.000Z","description":"猫，诗歌，精神动力学。艺术，朝闻道，波粒二象性。不断寻找着广播塔的星际候鸟。 | “我们彻夜飞旋，直至没入火焰。” | 匿名提问箱⬇️ | 🚪88/158","entities":{"url":{"urls":[{"display_url":"ngl.link/anincandescence","end":23,"expanded_url":"https://ngl.link/anincandescence","start":0,"url":"https://t.co/MuEKSg4tIS"}]}},"id":"1741993395910811648","location":"天鹅座X-1","name":"炽烈已极","pinned_tweet_id":"1944465960406245490","profile_image_url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1947176726292725760/VAZ0WSeY_normal.jpg","protected":false,"public_metrics":{"followers_count":1095,"following_count":205,"like_count":9579,"listed_count":1,"media_count":697,"tweet_count":3474},"url":"https://t.co/MuEKSg4tIS","username":"AnIncandescence","verified":f